sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin
    participant Frontend
    participant Backend
    participant Auth
    participant Controller
    participant DB

    Admin->>Frontend: Enter product details
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/products (Bearer)
    Backend->>Auth: Validate token + admin
    Auth-->>Backend: Authorized
    Backend->>Controller: createProduct
    Controller->>DB: Save product
    DB-->>Controller: Created product
    Controller-->>Backend: 201 Created
    Backend-->>Frontend: Product JSON
    Frontend-->>Admin: Show in catalogue
